# Form Design Instructions for frmSOWBuilderSingle

Since binary .frx files cannot be created directly as text, follow these instructions to manually set up the form controls in the VBA editor after creating the form:

## Form Properties
- Name: frmSOWBuilderSingle
- Caption: "SOW Builder"
- Width: 600
- Height: 500
- StartUpPosition: 1 - CenterOwner

